			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-8">
				<a href="https://github.com/notpepejulian/MySQL-BigchainDB" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-fuchsia-500 hover:bg-fuchsia-400 text-white font-semibold shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 text-base group">
